        <section>
            <h2>14. Consent</h2>
            <p>By downloading, installing, and using Annadanam Finder, you consent to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>The collection and use of your information as described in this Privacy Policy</li>
                <li>The processing of your data in accordance with this policy</li>
